data.description: Welcome to the exquisite Gatlin Creek, a meticulously crafted boutique community nestled in Georgetown and not far from Lake Georgetown, offering you the epitome of modern living with a remarkably low 1.9 percent tax rate.    Discover the unparalleled convenience of this prime location, just moments away from the upscale Wolf Ranch shopping center, ensuring that retail therapy and dining delights are always within easy reach. Immerse yourself in the vibrant energy of downtown Georgetown, where an array of dining and shopping options awaits, promising a lifestyle that effortlessly combines sophistication and convenience.    Indulge in the recreational pleasures provided by the nearby Jim Hogg Park on the shores of Lake Georgetown, offering the perfect retreat for boating and fishing enthusiasts. Gatlin Creek not only provides a home; it grants you access to a lifestyle tailored for those who appreciate both tranquility and adventure.    Step into this impeccably designed home built in 2020. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a generous 1888 square feet of living space, this residence is a harmonious blend of comfort and style. The interior is adorned with light wood-looking ceramic tile in the main areas, providing an inviting ambiance, while the bedrooms are graced with plush carpets for added warmth and coziness.    The heart of this home lies in its contemporary kitchen, adorned with pristine white quartz countertops and cabinets, creating an open and airy atmosphere that radiates both elegance and functionality. The result is a clean and bright aesthetic that sets the stage for delightful culinary experiences and memorable gatherings.    Experience the perfect balance of modern living and natural beauty in this thoughtfully designed community.
